text:
A family-run business led by a passionate couple, dedicated to delighting patrons with delicious food infused with their family's unique flavors and personal touch. With a diverse menu that changes daily, it's the perfect spot to relax and unwind with friends and family over satay at night. Private rooms are also available for small gatherings, with the option of catered food to complete the experience.

Best wishes for your growth!

The food is amazing! Especially the fried chicken! Thank you for serving us good food! :)
I bought Nasi lemak with fried chicken.The food taste was nice and super and it was in generous portion.
